ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this class to a student who has a project he/she would like to work on throughout the semester.
I would recommend the course as an excellent way to delve into a contemporary subject that one is interested in while having the opportunity to learn from exemplars of superb 21st century writing.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course is not completely academic in nature, and so it was excellent for preparing one for self-directed research, but not so useful otherwise. But that was not the aim of this course, and the space towork on other projects, tied into the dissertation but in another style, was much appreciated.
I'm not sure at this point, but I loved it.
